## Development

**Run Tests:**
```bash
pytest
```

## Security & Compliance
- **PolicyEnforcer**: Default fail-closed policy.
- **Audit Logs**: Stored in `logs/audit.log` (configurable).
- **Redaction**: Secrets (passwords, tokens) are automatically redacted from stdout/stderr.

